featured_reviews.review_id: Alhamdulillah (Glory to Allah) This is the masjid (Mosque) at Sihor area for five times prayers and Fridays Al Jumma prayer with rest room (Toilet) and water facilities five minutes walkable distance from Vijay palace hotel. Drinking water facilities are available.
